annotations.content: Go to sprint board and see assigned tasks
Does any task need code review?
Memorize the status of your tasks and get ready for scrum
Tell the status of each task at scrum meeting
Move the task to code review
Make a note of it and clarify it in scrum
Is there any task left from yesterday?
Is the task postponed in scrum call?
Update the status in that task
Pick up the next task assigned to you from sprint board
Do you need any clarification in that task?
PM Schedule appointment with customer/Team Lead
Go to sprint board and get the task ID
During commit write the task ID and summarize the work done
Assign the task to code review
Inform scrum master verbally if around
